{"tid":442010,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇高手可以教我將ielts writing由5.5升上6？","createTime":"2017-10-20T08:19:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-27T20:03:23.000Z","uid":27837,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"92cf6b32fac9a6fb29015e30c6f389f3e08ad30e","tid":442010,"uid":27837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T08:19:48.000Z","msg":"考左三次<br />\nOverall由5.5升到6.5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家L:7.5 R:6.5 S:6<br />\nWriting 就永遠都係5.5冇郁過<br />\n努力左好耐覺得上一次考嘅寫得幾好但係結果都得5.5<br />\n有冇巴絲可以提點下<br />\n已經跟晒格式寫法冇抄模板<br />\n可能我grammar唔好<br />\n<br />\n大家覺得我依家第表去申請學校讀語言班算數？<br />\n（如果差一個細項5.5語言班係唔係可以上比較短時間？）<br />\n定繼續考？但係writing唔似其他可以操卷操上去<br />\n淨係識自己一直寫一直寫 <br />\n 又唔知自己寫得好唔好<br />\n好似永遠都望唔到對安敢好無助<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nThanks"},{"pid":"c0c6d950de18662d7ab27e1d4f966cc48f8ba104","tid":442010,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T08:33:52.000Z","msg":"post篇野俾大家黎恥笑下先"},{"pid":"ecbfdb26b7d9d98bc8d86f0b27a8c73c55b66e66","tid":442010,"uid":27837,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T08:37:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>post篇野俾大家黎恥笑下先</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/20/163727_ac427402595f69ad607c29c2c2a06e70.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F20%2F163727_ac427402595f69ad607c29c2c2a06e70.jpg&h=7bd08d95&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/20/163729_c2b17d6a7be1e460e9e9d9267345fa2f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F20%2F163729_c2b17d6a7be1e460e9e9d9267345fa2f.jpg&h=3336311d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n高抬貴手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f417197caad31ac126c5a3ff6622d008644d011f","tid":442010,"uid":38623,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T08:40:11.000Z","msg":"想人幫手睇 連打出黎方便人睇都懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c11083152922462c8458496fe65380d92a82a86b","tid":442010,"uid":4880,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T08:56:32.000Z","msg":"cringy af<br />\n5.5 都好正常"},{"pid":"b5ad9913bc76d1dab9d264e4f247d291aa82c4ff","tid":442010,"uid":108132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T13:22:57.000Z","msg":"不如你自己重睇一次先。 我覺得就連段落舖排同表達都有小小問題<br />\n你自己睇一次就明"},{"pid":"3c83bd53cd85c5681ca4724cb691ee4d79d563e1","tid":442010,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T09:24:13.000Z","msg":"Cambrige IELTS Past Paper 1-10 download link<br />\n<a href=\"http://skpan.com/ls/queenays/cd871105\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fskpan.com%2Fls%2Fqueenays%2Fcd871105&d=A7kOZpoo0mE6aRkvZ0BVTRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=6ab3a374\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://skpan.com/ls/queenays/cd871105</a>"},{"pid":"2a8bb083dd1b2de35abffff1fa905caedb03bd83","tid":442010,"uid":79891,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T12:45:30.000Z","msg":"可唔可以教下你點由5.5升到6.5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cda84d48b50b05c7e80b67472e2f0caff32a9e97","tid":442010,"uid":137569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T13:15:16.000Z","msg":"我w6.5 o6 r7.5 l7<br />\n因想移民，需要四條七，但真係好難考<br />\n而家半年無考，好驚不進反退<br />\n諗緊去唔去讀啲oral同寫作班"},{"pid":"ddd5d36c77e9ddc994a1d569141e36fc5d86fe58","tid":442010,"uid":119145,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T15:49:09.000Z","msg":"最大死症：<br />\n1, grammar錯到...太明顯，你可以錯grammar但唔好錯咁明顯plz,一眼就睇到<br />\n2, 太多串錯字<br />\n3,寫太多廢話都未講到重點，好似純粹表現緊你，完全冇意義，做到呢點可以6.5<br />\n頭2點先係上唔到6既重大死症"},{"pid":"427ecd97e1db93eb4d7bcfdaa7be99784079b97f","tid":442010,"uid":67744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T15:53:23.000Z","msg":"我當年中七去考都係5.5，之後大學final year去考就有6<br />\n<br />\n都係靠操多d，識多d生字，改下寫作技巧同結構，listening就靠操多d，oral就搵d鬼佬傾下計"},{"pid":"93c264a54a7df7c50a52e49388c3b00ed13ea0d1","tid":442010,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T15:58:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"07ce8f6f98cdc2c7ac5ce6bc3d226ab9ceb6a20b","tid":442010,"uid":107503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T16:02:32.000Z","msg":"你每句都寫得好長 不斷用comma 好似死唔斷氣咁"},{"pid":"e069727709a63520d41b6eb63a60618e68d17560","tid":442010,"uid":117855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T16:11:55.000Z","msg":"你中文作文掂唔掂架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e5cf4a6f706e3df251e9b7a90b0c2d676fd6cd0","tid":442010,"uid":111627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T16:12:39.000Z","msg":"你第一段都好有問題 一睇就知6分打起<br />\n再睇埋下段 已經唔想睇 <br />\n你唔好背咁多framework <br />\n太DSE 唔係IELTS 要嘅野<br />\n睇下每本書最後嘅範文<br />\n利申 得7分Dominiccc"},{"pid":"8381398f12242c8a846b400ad4196f84cfd03749","tid":442010,"uid":38623,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T01:58:09.000Z","msg":"Writing 無溫過拎7.5 , 有加紙, 諗到咩就寫咩, 除左英文能力, 都要言之有物，唔係咩phrase都用就得 <br />\nwriting呢份卷係好奇怪，我有個fd英文好我非常多（佢DGS）writing 都係拎7"},{"pid":"eab88deeb114e37dbd0c8d970e4862d2fdc30b83","tid":442010,"uid":72228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T19:57:40.000Z","msg":"好多罐頭句 係咪街外course教你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09c6cdb2e41f15708713c647ec2a5ee23c786c23","tid":442010,"uid":47378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T20:03:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Writing 無溫過拎7.5 , 有加紙, 諗到咩就寫咩, 除左英文能力, 都要言之有物，唔係咩phrase都用就得 <br />\nwriting呢份卷係好奇怪，我有個fd英文好我非常多（佢DGS）writing 都係拎7</blockquote><br />\nwriting 同 speaking 其實都係 content &gt; grammar (當然都唔可以太柒)<br />\n啲問題如果你連用中文答都未必答得好，當然會低分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申"},{"pid":"40614c8ee9a56c575f8ab410daa560fe49260be7","tid":442010,"uid":47378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T20:03:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Writing 無溫過拎7.5 , 有加紙, 諗到咩就寫咩, 除左英文能力, 都要言之有物，唔係咩phrase都用就得 <br />\nwriting呢份卷係好奇怪，我有個fd英文好我非常多（佢DGS）writing 都係拎7</blockquote><br />\nwriting 同 speaking 其實都係 content &gt; grammar (當然都唔可以太柒)<br />\n啲問題如果你連用中文答都未必答得好，當然會低分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申低分</blockquote>"}]}